    <entry>
      <title>java学习路线1</title>
      <link href="/java-xue-xi-lu-xian-1/"/>
      <url>/java-xue-xi-lu-xian-1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>java学习路线之<strong>java语言</strong>，核心知识点……</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="1-语言基础"><a href="#1-语言基础" class="headerlink" title="1.语言基础"></a>1.语言基础</h1><h2 id="1-1-面向对象"><a href="#1-1-面向对象" class="headerlink" title="1.1 面向对象"></a>1.1 面向对象</h2><h3 id="封装"><a href="#封装" class="headerlink" title="封装"></a>封装</h3><p>封装即是抽象，对于抽象出来的东西可做到权限的管控，可暴露、可隐藏。概念比较简单，不赘述。</p><h3 id="继承"><a href="#继承" class="headerlink" title="继承"></a>继承</h3><p>就如同继承家业、继承资产一样，子类继承了父类，可以使用父类所有能力。父子类之间是“<strong>属于</strong>”关系(is-a关系)</p><h3 id="多态"><a href="#多态" class="headerlink" title="多态"></a>多态</h3><h4 id="1-什么是多态？"><a href="#1-什么是多态？" class="headerlink" title="1.什么是多态？"></a>1.什么是多态？</h4><p>借用网友的话说，</p><blockquote><p>多态是同一个行为具有多个不同表现形式或形态的能力。</p><p>多态就是同一个接口，使用不同的实例而执行不同操作。</p><p>​                                                                            —–<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/scyq/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MelonChen’s Blog</a></p></blockquote><p>多态又分为：编译时多态(比如重载)和运行时多态(比如重写)。判断多态是否存在，需要满足以下三个条件：</p><p>1.是否存在继承关系；</p><p>2.子类是否重写了父类的方法；</p><p>3.父类的引用是否指向了子类的对象；    </p><p><img src="/java-xue-xi-lu-xian-1/duotai.jpg" alt="多态形象描述"></p><h4 id="2-实现机制是啥？"><a href="#2-实现机制是啥？" class="headerlink" title="2.实现机制是啥？"></a>2.实现机制是啥？</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-wiki"><code class="language-wiki">void foo(String str);void foo(int number);<span class="token hr punctuation">------</span>一个方法名，参数不同，这叫方法重载。(Overload),父类与子类有同样的方法名和参数，这叫方法覆盖。(Override)<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>子类虽然继承了父类，但是父类的方法可能并不适用子类，此时子类可以选择覆盖（override）。如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Animal</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> num <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">static</span>  <span class="token keyword">int</span> age <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">30</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"动物吃饭"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">sleep</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"动物睡觉"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">run</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"动物会奔跑"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Dog</span> <span class="token keyword">extends</span> <span class="token class-name">Animal</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> num <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span>  age <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">100</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    String name <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"旺财"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token annotation punctuation">@Override</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"狗吃饭"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">sleep</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"狗在睡觉ing"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">TestDemo</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        Animal am <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Dog</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        am<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        am<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">sleep</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        am<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">run</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>am<span class="token punctuation">.</span>num<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>am<span class="token punctuation">.</span>age<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>运行结果：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-wiki"><code class="language-wiki">狗吃饭动物睡觉动物会奔跑2030<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>父类或者接口定义的引用变量可以指向子类或者具体实现类的实例对象，由于<strong>程序调用方法是在运行期才动态绑定</strong>的，那么引用变量所指向的具体实例对象在运行期才确定。所以这个对象的方法是运行期正在内存运行的这个对象的方法而不是引用变量的类型中定义的方法。</p><h4 id="3-总结"><a href="#3-总结" class="headerlink" title="3.总结"></a>3.总结</h4><p><strong>成员变量</strong><br>编译看左边（基类），运行看左边（基类）；无论如何都是访问基类的成员变量。<br><strong>成员方法</strong><br>编译看左边（基类），运行看右边（派生类），动态绑定。<br><strong>Static方法</strong><br>编译看左边（基类），运行看左边（基类）。<br><em>只有非静态的成员方法,编译看左边,运行看右边。不能使用派生类特有的成员属性和派生类特有的成员方法。</em></p><h4 id="4-参考文章"><a href="#4-参考文章" class="headerlink" title="4.参考文章"></a>4.参考文章</h4><p>1.<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/68ddb5484ca2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">什么是多态？实现多态的机制是什么？</a></p><p>2.<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/30082151/answer/120520568" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JAVA的多态用几句话能直观的解释一下吗？</a></p><h2 id="1-2-容器"><a href="#1-2-容器" class="headerlink" title="1.2 容器"></a>1.2 容器</h2><h2 id="1-3-异常"><a href="#1-3-异常" class="headerlink" title="1.3 异常"></a>1.3 异常</h2><h2 id="1-4-泛型"><a href="#1-4-泛型" class="headerlink" title="1.4 泛型"></a>1.4 泛型</h2><h2 id="1-5-反射"><a href="#1-5-反射" class="headerlink" title="1.5 反射"></a>1.5 反射</h2><h2 id="1-6-注解"><a href="#1-6-注解" class="headerlink" title="1.6 注解"></a>1.6 注解</h2><h2 id="1-7-I-O"><a href="#1-7-I-O" class="headerlink" title="1.7 I/O"></a>1.7 I/O</h2><h2 id="1-8-swing"><a href="#1-8-swing" class="headerlink" title="1.8 swing"></a><del>1.8 swing</del></h2><h1 id="2-jvm"><a href="#2-jvm" class="headerlink" title="2.jvm"></a>2.jvm</h1><h2 id="2-1-类加载机制"><a href="#2-1-类加载机制" class="headerlink" title="2.1 类加载机制"></a>2.1 类加载机制</h2><h2 id="2-2-java内存模型"><a href="#2-2-java内存模型" class="headerlink" title="2.2 java内存模型"></a>2.2 java内存模型</h2><h2 id="2-3-GC垃圾回收"><a href="#2-3-GC垃圾回收" class="headerlink" title="2.3 GC垃圾回收"></a>2.3 GC垃圾回收</h2><h2 id="2-4-JVM性能监控与故障定位"><a href="#2-4-JVM性能监控与故障定位" class="headerlink" title="2.4 JVM性能监控与故障定位"></a>2.4 JVM性能监控与故障定位</h2><h1 id="3-多线程-并发"><a href="#3-多线程-并发" class="headerlink" title="3.多线程/并发"></a>3.多线程/并发</h1><h2 id="3-1-并发编程基础"><a href="#3-1-并发编程基础" class="headerlink" title="3.1 并发编程基础"></a>3.1 并发编程基础</h2><h3 id="线程创建"><a href="#线程创建" class="headerlink" title="线程创建"></a>线程创建</h3><h3 id="关键字基础"><a href="#关键字基础" class="headerlink" title="关键字基础"></a>关键字基础</h3><h3 id="基础概念"><a href="#基础概念" class="headerlink" title="基础概念"></a>基础概念</h3><h2 id="3-2-线程池"><a href="#3-2-线程池" class="headerlink" title="3.2 线程池"></a>3.2 线程池</h2><h2 id="3-3-锁"><a href="#3-3-锁" class="headerlink" title="3.3 锁"></a>3.3 锁</h2><h2 id="3-4-并发容器"><a href="#3-4-并发容器" class="headerlink" title="3.4 并发容器"></a>3.4 并发容器</h2><h2 id="3-5-原子类"><a href="#3-5-原子类" class="headerlink" title="3.5 原子类"></a>3.5 原子类</h2><h2 id="3-6-JUC并发工具类"><a href="#3-6-JUC并发工具类" class="headerlink" title="3.6 JUC并发工具类"></a>3.6 JUC并发工具类</h2>]]></content>
      
      
